  "description": "A large container ship, identifiable as the 'APORE' with vibrant orange, blue and white coloration, is being guided by a tugboat through a channel of water. The ship's hull is covered in stacked shipping containers, creating a textured and colorful wall. In the background, the iconic red structure of the Golden Gate Bridge is visible, spanning a wide waterway. The water is choppy with visible waves and wakes from the vessels. The sky is overcast and a pale blue-grey. A crane is visible on the far right, suggesting a port or harbor setting. Distant hills and landmasses frame the background.",
